om/public/images/0f0871fd-e098-4c65-b588-25be6751782b_3278x3508.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5dea62c9-a0ce-422c-8298-40a2c296c496_2899x4100.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1d5c03db-a066-426b-b05f-66a421495e67_3238x4000.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/26ec1a83-7614-4af3-b174-738a711f70e9_6000x4000.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/65de1233-0041-4b58-8c97-311067c32f71_6000x4000.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ac9883dc-5719-49c6-b099-851f0ea11bdc_6000x4000.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9af06f8e-44e2-4227-b7a3-f241a4dd926a_6000x4000.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;1,2,3. Claudia Lemke 4. Hana Earle 5, 6. Joline Uvman 7. Nicola Blumenthal&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/55492046-213f-4dd3-99bb-9957b052395e_1456x1946.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}\"></div><div class=\"image-gallery-embed\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/990b107e-5f7b-41f3-90cd-4875c148cfe3_2875x3547.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/48a9f1c1-c0bf-4b3e-a8d8-3bad439541c7_5000x3877.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b42a9420-91b3-4f77-b7d2-8b418ec8fc7b_1663x2745.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/91f9d2f8-1915-43a8-8b14-44898eecc298_3665x4000.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/79a974d9-404f-47a8-a4ae-268285d936b2_6000x4000.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f5fff6c3-87f3-475b-ae8f-b66cf66c4026_6000x4000.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/08ee0d3c-534f-4292-8091-4c8c67ac4d56_6000x4000.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;8. Nicola Blumenthal 9, 10, 11, 12, 13, 14. Nina Zeljković&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f1b1af9f-b613-4491-b949-9f4bf69d5565_1456x1946.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}\"></div><p>I curated this group show with Nicola Blumenthal, Claudia Lemke, Nina Zeljković, Hana Earles, Joline Uvman. We had a great opening, the works are beautiful. You can check out this archive, also hosted on <a href=\"https://vtre.cc/exhibition/stooj-fine-arts-social-society\">vtre.cc</a> , and eventually on <a href=\"https://www.stooge.eu/\">Stooj</a> Fine Arts Co.</p><p>Jeff made a video tour of this exhibition, as well as a video document of me performing my exhibition text, to be added to this blog entry at a later date. - C.B. July 14, 2026</p>"
