      "title": "Documentation of my work at Eden: Wet Work Over Lap, at Kim(?) - 5/29 to 7/11/26",
      "link": "https://cammisabuerhaus.substack.com/p/test-post",
      "pubDate": "2026-07-13T16:53:19.595Z",
      "description": "Photography, flatwork, collage, and film.",
      "content": "<p>This show closed only a few days ago, July 11, 2026. Working with curator Zane Onckule and the Kim team was a pleasure. I’d love to go back to Riga. What a cool city and so close to the Baltic sea, which I'd never seen before. </p><p>I contributed five works to this, my first institutional group show, a series of silver gelatins, a collage, a uv print, my film <em>After Discipline</em>, and performance. The image gallery below lays out how the show was installed spatially. </p><p>I’ll add photos and video of my May 29th performance, Bookwoman, at the end of this post on another day. <br><sub>- C.B., July 14, 2026</sub><br></p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x